         * "rayban_meta", "rayban_display", "oakley_meta_hstn",
         * "oakley_meta_vanguard", "rayban_meta_optics". Open vocabulary (same
         * rationale as `vendor`; shells type it as `GlassesDeviceType`). `None`
         * until the transport learns the model. The closed [`DeviceType`] enum
